  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capt Crabs, the pirate crab, was out with his crew searching for treasure on a mysterious island when suddenly his ship was taken by some mischievous slimes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now he's on a mission to retrieve his ship and treasure and get back to the pirate life he loves!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406630/extras/d2baf296f4b519180eb6b0f27223aa82.avif?t=1770072745\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capt Crabs is a family friendly, fun, mario-esk type platformer with lots of fun gameplay, an in-game currency store (NOT micro-transactions) for costumes and weapons and loads of funny situations to encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406630/extras/bce2b10a16bc6336aa0bb7685decfd12.avif?t=1770072745\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is filled with all kinds of fun slimes, friendly and enemy, to encounter as well as creative boss battles and adventures to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406630/extras/9c5a6fb3736184beb9bbc2f88f57bbec.avif?t=1770072745\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capt Crabs, the pirate crab, was out with his crew searching for treasure on a mysterious island when suddenly his ship was taken by some mischievous slimes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now he's on a mission to retrieve his ship and treasure and get back to the pirate life he loves!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406630/extras/d2baf296f4b519180eb6b0f27223aa82.avif?t=1770072745\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capt Crabs is a family friendly, fun, mario-esk type platformer with lots of fun gameplay, an in-game currency store (NOT micro-transactions) for costumes and weapons and loads of funny situations to encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406630/extras/bce2b10a16bc6336aa0bb7685decfd12.avif?t=1770072745\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is filled with all kinds of fun slimes, friendly and enemy, to encounter as well as creative boss battles and adventures to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406630/extras/9c5a6fb3736184beb9bbc2f88f57bbec.avif?t=1770072745\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p>",
